---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</h1>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="terminal-block">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="dot red"></span>
        <span class="dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">user@verification-hell</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <p><span class="prompt">$</span> cat ~/.profile</p>
        <pre class="output">
NAME="A Frustrated Business Owner"
LOCATION="Somewhere Google Can't Verify"
STATUS="Permanently Pending Verification"
MOOD="Increasingly Unhinged"
        </pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Why This Blog Exists</h2>
    
    <p>
      I started this blog to document my ongoing battle with Google's business 
      verification system. What should have been a simple process—proving that 
      my legitimate, physical business exists—turned into a months-long 
      odyssey of rejected verifications, phantom postcards, and support 
      tickets that vanish into the void.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you've found this blog, chances are you're experiencing similar 
      frustrations. You're not alone. You're not crazy. The system is 
      genuinely broken.
    </p>

    <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time documentation of my verification attempts</li>
      <li>Screenshots of absurd error messages and rejections</li>
      <li>Attempts to find workarounds (spoiler: there aren't many)</li>
      <li>Occasional existential despair</li>
      <li>Maybe, eventually, success? (Don't hold your breath)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    
    <p>
      Want to share your own Google Business horror story? 
      Feel free to reach out. Misery loves company.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-info">
      <p><span class="label">Email:</span> your-email@example.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .terminal-block {
    background: var(--bg-terminal);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: #2d2d2d;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .dot.green { background: #27ca40; }

  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .terminal-body p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #00ff41;
  }

  .terminal-body .output {
    color: #8be9fd;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .terminal-body .prompt {
    color: #ff79c6;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-info .label {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
